column5: Has anyone been up to Cedar lake/Cross bay Manitoba lately? Just wondering how the bite has been during this heat....I'm on my way next week!

its been a weird year the walleye's started to bite late this year.And with this heat we are still getting 40 to 60 fish days.Hope the lakers are biting i'm heading for 3 days to Reed lake,and tramping for walleye's.FISH ON.
to the top -and only 2 more sleeps.......
